    • initialize

      public void initialize​(java.net.URL location, java.util.ResourceBundle resources)
      This function executes as soon as the the class is created. It initializes the TableView containing the projects and its columns, and lists the appropriate projects. It also sets a listener on the TableView in order to know when the user clicks on a certain project.
      Specified by:
      initialize in interface javafx.fxml.Initializable
